{"id": "1341702469285187618", "channel_id": "1339926772770410518", "type": 19, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "你好守密人，很抱歉讓您產生這樣的印象。其實有問必答當中的所有問題，戈雅都有回報給到校工的，只是有一些需要校工定位到問題所在，或者說有明朗的解法之後，戈雅才給到回復~<:wish:1236951537788649492>", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T09:26:36.304000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["594196021119287316"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "👀", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1341696647226327051", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1339926772770410518", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.1.0.2 停服維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1341716840845676675", "channel_id": "1339926772770410518", "type": 19, "author_id": "1341406859411587215", "author_name": "stariver_i", "author_bot": false, "content": "那问你们到底打不打算回调或者修改的问题还得多久才能定位到问题所在啊👀", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T10:23:42.751000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1341702469285187618", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1339926772770410518", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.1.0.2 停服維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1341753455781613632", "channel_id": "1339926772770410518", "type": 19, "author_id": "1327196036321640469", "author_name": "nidie0256_61327", "author_bot": false, "content": "核心问题就两个判断题：\n是否回调机制或者怪的数值？\n是否有正经补偿？对于你们给玩家提供这种bug满天飞、体验极其恶劣的测试服版本？\nDouble No的话就可以尊重祝福、人生有梦各自精彩了。", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T12:49:12.432000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1341702469285187618", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1339926772770410518", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.1.0.2 停服維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1341835744167202866", "channel_id": "1339926772770410518", "type": 19, "author_id": "1262202061227950102", "author_name": "inklk1104", "author_bot": false, "content": "核心问题大伙都已经提出来好久了，我们也相信戈雅有好好传达，但是校猫那边如果铁了心想装死其实也可以直接说 对大伙都好，毕竟他这么干也不是一次两次了不是吗？", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T18:16:11.512000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1131790839291596841"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1341702469285187618", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1339926772770410518", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.1.0.2 停服維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1341836223576014989", "channel_id": "1339926772770410518", "type": 0, "author_id": "1262202061227950102", "author_name": "inklk1104", "author_bot": false, "content": "倒不如说比起装死 校猫一直以来的态度 做的事 才是最让大伙火大的 玩家对你们的信赖都快透支完了才出来做什么所谓的解释可是一点用都没有的", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T18:18:05.812000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1339926772770410518", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.1.0.2 停服維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
{"id": "1341836641311916155", "channel_id": "1339926772770410518", "type": 0, "author_id": "1262202061227950102", "author_name": "inklk1104", "author_bot": false, "content": "之前1.0打赢复活赛说的那些话跟放屁一样晃一眼就过去了，现在依然在一意孤行恶心所有人 麻烦转告一下，如果还嫌节奏不够大大可以继续装死 等冷处理成功了看看还剩多少人，我等着看玩家还有多少耐心给你们", "timestamp": "2025-02-19T18:19:45.408000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1339926772770410518", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.1.0.2 停服維護公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080"]}
